Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:04.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The conditions for Sir Hero to return to his homeworld
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:07.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,have really been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has been working so hard for everyone,\Nbut now all those memories will be wiped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is definitely something wrong with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:19.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a sad ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:11.40,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(400,1000)\pos(124,353)}  「Promise」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)}I can't eat any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.69,0:02:38.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it be until your summer holiday starts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. If we go according to Earth time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:46.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,today is the 4th of April, so about a hundred days, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:51.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss you a lot if it's that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:55.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I visit for two or three days,\Nthen I can come during short breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:59.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's an emergency, please call me anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Thanks, Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:06.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,must we really perform the ceremony today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:10.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't miss it! 'Cause you're Sink the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:14.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The deportation ceremony has to be a grand affair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:20.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti's hero, Sink, has accomplished the mission he was summoned for,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so today he'll be returning to his homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:29.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pass the Holy Sword, Palladion, to Princess Millhiore, your summoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit more. {I feel a powerful surge of emotions when I see Rico like this. I'll be mad if Rico's crying face is release SS. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:02.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait for me just a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a way that we don't \Nhave to part painfully with Sir Hero. {AL: say a sad goodbye... or something.. i can't find any words in english to make it ... real like}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:11.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I finish reading this page, and I get a little more information,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just might find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:33.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:41.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really... useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:49.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been trying so hard, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:53.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won't be able to bring back the memory of anything at all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:58.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but, even so, I'll never forget anything!{AL: he said "but" twice.. previously and this line if you feel it's weird, then change it if you want}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely remember it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:07.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:07.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A four-colored ball point pen and portable speakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can give you my cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:20.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but these should be good enough for you to have fun disassembling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:24.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the heart... to disassemble them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat them with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever and ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! I can't believe I still have\Nto escort you on your last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad that you're the one seeing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:55.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess is already at the \Nlocation prepared for the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:58.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't take our sweet time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Eclair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though this isn't brand new,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:09.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will you still accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll just keep it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:14.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it looks like you've given everyone a little something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:19.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:25.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave both Lady d'Arquien and the Leader of Knights a memento coin from my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave Yuki my cell phone strap, and what's left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if you're giving parting gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:44.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be true. Once you're deported, you can't come back to Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:45.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:55.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like... I'll lose all my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories about the days I had here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:06:59.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would have guessed from Rico's expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:09.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I heard it was real easy for you to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew it'd end up like this when you went back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:20.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I won't forget everything \Nthat happened here in Flonyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or all that I've gone through with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:27.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember the captain who easily gets angry but \Nforgives instantly, who is strong and straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All that I've experienced with you, Eclair...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:38.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not confident I'll remember you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:43.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The training. The battles. The diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll feel so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If being forgotten makes you lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't want to be forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:59.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then no matter what happens, don't forget all of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:04.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then... come back as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:08.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:40.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tatsumaki. You came too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:44.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, he wanted to see you off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:53.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Sink and I can be here during the moment of deportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:56.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumaki, why don't you bid Sink goodbye right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thank you too, Tatsumaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:09.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While waiting for you, I completed the ceremony's preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, it'll be the opposite of how you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll ascend to the sky from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:18.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you'll return to your homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:32.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be just a short while ago that I summoned you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:36.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,yet it feels like it's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:41.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you here, and you became our hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:46.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So much has happened, but most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:50.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you came here, and I got along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:55.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun. Really, really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:02.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I had so much fun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:07.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting summoned to Biscotti. Being with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:12.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry, I'll definitely return during summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:23.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be... a lot, lot more exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:28.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:31.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we'll definitely, definitely meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:36.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't forget about you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't forget about us either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:45.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't! Definitely won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:46.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:10.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:26.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink... Sink! Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:32.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want you to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:40.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to stay with you, \Nforever and ever together with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay with you and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:56.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Millhi, will forever and ever love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:12.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, I love you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll definitely come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:20.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return and see you again! I promise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, are you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:59.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:08.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:17.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least respond to me. Or did you just wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:22.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:27.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aching anywhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means, in conclusion, that's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the beginning of spring break two weeks ago, you remember you went somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't remember where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:45.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, somehow, you feel like something really sad happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That too, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:56.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, Memory Loss, Concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! 84,000 search results?! {Can be made 84000, as it's displayed for short time and the number is big. -sm}{The comma is good. -Anigel}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:03.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hey! There's no need to check. I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I got a head injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:09.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it? I just can't seem to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:12.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But shouldn't we go to the hospital for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better if you have a checkup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no need. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:21.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your trip? Shouldn't you contact your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:26.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Becky, but I'm really okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go after breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:37.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I feel that I was really happy before this.{After experimenting with the end of line many times, I decided to end it here. Please change if necessary. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:47.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I heard you can also have memories of weird stuff when you encounter sudden forgetfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be good if that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:59.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm just an ordinary first year middle school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:05.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with my neighbor, my caring best friend, Becky,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:09.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in my second year as soon as spring break ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink! Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:19.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forget Nanami, my relative, master, and rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:26.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are still as cute as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the only long-awaited greeting that we get?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, kiss me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:36.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami never really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her dad is an oceanographer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and her mom is a marine biologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:55.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never forgotten all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... what's this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:15:59.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:06.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm forgetting something really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:12.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like something very important has been taken away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:15.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an uneasy feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Did I wake you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:41.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know the issue of Sink's return would be so complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had realized it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what he wished for, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:53.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These were taken from Galette's library.\NThey are books about summonings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:02.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This seal... Doesn't this\Nbelong to Biscotti's leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.83,Location Names,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}To the National Research Academy of Biscotti, with regards to hero summoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:15.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are things you should pay \Nattention to when sending the hero back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:25.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Deportation is only used when the hero wishes to resign from his position with the person who summoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:32.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When this happens, the hero will not be able to take anything from Flonyard, including memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:42.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, these memories will not immediately vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:46.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon deportation, the hero will enter a locked condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:52.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A time frame of six months is needed for the memories to be completely erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:18:00.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, in order to summon the returned hero, the below conditions need to be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:08.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One, the hero can be re-summoned for ninety days from the time he was first summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:16.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two, the hero needs to make a promise to three people aside from the summoner to return to Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:22.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make that covenant, the hero has to entrust his belongings to these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:30.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what the belongings are, though it is better for the items to be from the hero's homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:42.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for disturbing you this early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:47.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:50.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were entrusted with something from Sir Hero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:58.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the ceremony ended, Sink said he \Nhoped that I would open this after he went back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:01.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is, then it will be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:16.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...he has to entrust a covenant item, a proof of promise to return to the summoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:24.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The proof of promise must clearly state the interval of return, the hero and the summoner's name. {period; term; interval}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:30.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To my respected princess, Millhiore Frianno Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:35.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hero Sink Izumi, express my greatest gratitude, love, and friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:42.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,P.S. I'll definitely come back as a hero! This I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:47.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:50.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, it's all possible now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:53.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can summon the hero once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:56.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:20:02.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Sir Hero really has kept his promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:53.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:59.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky! Becky! Becky! Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:00.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.60,Dialogue Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky!{Hopefully this takes care of so many "Becky!"s in a nice way, please change if necessary. -sm}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:03.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Sink, Sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh! What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:12.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered! I remembered everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:13.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a really interesting place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:20.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a lot of fun! I made a lot of friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:22.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:26.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break! Becky, let's go there together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:29.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, okay. Well, I'll go if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink, Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:37.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are having fun alone. I want to join in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:57.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During the spring break between our first and second years, I was a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:01.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a hero again... during summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:05.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}I'm going to that world again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:33.29,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,00)\blur5}I couldn't forget the color of the sky the two of us gazed upon that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:45.66,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,00)\blur10}Everyone started running together, full of dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:51.68,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,00)\blur5}This isn't "farewell," as I will meet you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:56.54,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,500)\blur5}Because this wish will be fulfilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:23:03.48,Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,500)\blur5}Let's embrace these warm memories of ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:07.89,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,500)\blur5}memories of the days we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:16.79,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,500)\blur5}I will fulfill the promise we made when we held hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:26.73,Romaji2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(500,500)\blur5}No matter how long it takes, I will be right here waiting for you.
